Use the standard library
This is how to is_prime of n:
  When n is less than 2, then:
    The answer is 0
  End when
  Do this n times:
    Remember that i is sum of i and 1
    When i is less than 2, then:
      Do nothing
    End when
    When i is at most n, then:
      When remainder of n and i is 0, then:
        The answer is 0
      End when
    End when
  End do
  The answer is 1
Now you know